tags.name: wave-player
tags.description:
`wave-player`

Attributes:

  * `src` {`string`} - The source of the audio file to be played

  * `title` {`string`} - The main (bold) title

  * `subtitle` {`string`} - The smaller subtitle, for chapter heading or composer.

  * `coverart` {`string`} - The sourse for cover art

  * `wavesurfer` - container for the wave object

  * `lean` {`string`} - Determines if the FOB is on the left or the right

  * `wavecolor` {`string`} - Color of the Wave

  * `progresscolor` {`string`} - Color of the completed section of the wave

Properties:

  * `wavecolor` {`string`} - Color of the Wave

  * `progresscolor` {`string`} - Color of the completed section of the wave

  * `_template` {`HTMLTemplateElement | null`} -
